"Color scheme
color jellybeans

"Tab switching
map <D-A-left> gT
map <D-A-right> gt
map <D-1> 1gt
map <D-2> 2gt
map <D-3> 3gt
map <D-4> 4gt
map <D-5> 5gt
map <D-6> 6gt
map <D-7> 7gt
map <D-8> 8gt
map <D-9> 9gt
map <D-0> 10gt

"Auto-reload this file on save
autocmd! bufwritepost .gvimrc.after source ~/.gvimrc.after